      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for your next project or a budget-friendly fixer-upper? This car is in poor condition and will need some dedicated TLC to get it back to its best, but it offers a fantastic foundation for anyone looking for a rewarding mechanical challenge! It's priced to sell and ready for a new owner who isn't afraid to roll up their sleeves and bring this diamond in the rough back to life.",
